    {
      "para_id": "Q001027.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(i 1) Ur-Nanše , king of Lagaš , child of Gunidu , citizen of Gursar , built the shrine of Ĝirsu ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001027.8",
      "line_range": "8",
      "translation": "(ii 3) He fashioned ( the statue of ) Šul-šagana . He fashioned ( the statue of ) Gušudu . He fashioned ( the statue of ) Kindazid.He built the temple of Ninmarki . He fashioned ( the statue of ) Lama-u-e ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001027.18",
      "line_range": "18",
      "translation": "(iii 7) He dug the A-suhur-canal . He dug the Eg-tirsig-canal . He dug the great ... of the Enlile-pada-canal . He dug the ... of the Surdugin-du-canal . He dug the Nin-REC107-ba-du ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001027.30",
      "line_range": "30",
      "translation": "(v 5) He is a man , who submits to the orders of Nanše ."
    }
  ],
